+# Frontend-only Voting App (Vue 3)
+
+- Vue 3 + Composition API + `<script setup>`
+- Pinia state management with LocalStorage persistence
+- No backend, no external APIs
+
+## Dev
+
+```bash
+cd repository_after
+npm install
+npm run dev -- --host
+```
+
+## Build
+
+```bash
+npm run build
+npm run preview -- --host
+```
